#### Get a Movie
GET {{base}}/movies/{{movie.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

#### Updates a Movie
PUT {{base}}/movies/{{movie.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "spider man",
