#### List Movies
GET {{base}}/movies
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

#### List Movies with Page
GET {{base}}/movies?page=0&size=2
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

#### Get a Movie
DELETE {{base}}/movies/{{movie.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

#### Get as User
POST {{base}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json